Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 17:52:29 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(funnel): add marketing landing + pricing surface

Add a sales funnel as the first surface after the legal gate:
- LandingScreen: hero, value props and pricing for new visitors
- Pricing: Free vs Premium with monthly/annual toggle, wired to the
  existing auth/checkout seam (startCheckout)
- App: one-time "entered" gate (localStorage); premium users skip it
- TopBar: "Planes" entry that opens an in-app pricing overlay

Placeholder prices are clearly marked for editing.
